"{\"uid\": \"krcrtv.com-news-local-join-the-fun-special-olympics-hosts-weekend-tournament-in-shasta-county\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Now  44\\u00b0  Fri  66\\u00b0  Sat  61\\u00b0  byMarion Rodriguez    SHASTA COUNTY, Calif. -The Special Olympics Shasta County (SOSC) will be hosting two events over the weekend for persons with intellectual disabilities.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to their Facebook post, a dinner and dance will be held on Friday, Sept. 20 from 6-8:30 p.m. at the Frontier Senior Center in Anderson.On Saturday, Sept. 21 they will be holding a bowling tournament at Shasta Lanes starting at 8:30 a.m.  SOSC said lunch will be provided for all athletes and volunteers, and medals will be awarded later in the day.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Shasta\", \"score\": 0.6701357849092393, \"rank\": 0.4531249853179361, \"text\": \"Shasta\", \"types\": [\"Q8072\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Shasta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Shasta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These events come on the heels of some more fun where the athletes competed at the Yuba city regional softball competition earning silver medals.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuba_River\", \"score\": 0.9999993694917462, \"rank\": 6.259191518388483e-07, \"text\": \"Yuba\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuba_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuba_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Northstate's NewsNazy Javidcongratulated the teams on Daybreak.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, you can visit the Special Olympics Shasta County Facebook pagehere.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025Sinclair, Inc.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": []}]}"